1. Introduction & Core Objective
I need a Flutter + Firebase app for a private financial group ("RD Group"). The app manages monthly contributions, loans, and strict penalties for 22 specific members. My Contact: [Yahan Apna Email ID Dalein] | Phone number available upon request for serious developers.

